QuestData.Title: Seeing Orange
QuestData.Description: Those virmen... they make me do horrible, horrible, silly things. All involving carrots. I couldn't tell you how many carrots they threw at me.$b$bLet's not waste any more time. Get me out of here!
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Mina Mudclaw back home to her father.
QuestData.RewardText: What's all this fuss about carrots? I don't get it.

Objectives.Objective: Bring Mina Mudclaw home to her father
